<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0px;/*This removes the border around the canvas that Phaser adds, making the game actually take up all the available space*/
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: lighter;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            background: black;
        }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #1e2e4f;
        }
        canvas {
            max-width: 100vw;
            max-height: 100vh;
        }
        .toubleshoot {
            width: 50vw;
            margin: 0 auto;

        }
        .hidden {
            display: none;
        }
        h1, h3, p, ul, li {
            color: white !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class='toubleshoot' id='troubleshoot'>
        <h1>R0d3nt is loading...</h1>
        <p>If you're seeing this, the game is going through initial loading.
            <br>
            It should dissapear in a moment.
        </p>
        <hr>
        <h3>Troubleshooting</h3>
        <p>If it's not dissapearing and/or nothing is happening :</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Do you have an ad-Blocker? Try whitelisting this page (there's no ads here I swear)</li>
            <li>Slow connection? You'll have to wait a moment <br> Try refreshing if it takes too long</li>
        </ul>
        <p>There <b>is</b> downloadable version of the game on <a href='https://tuskat.itch.io/r0d3nt'>itch.io page</a>. Download it if nothing else work.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
